properties.areaDesc: Los Angeles County San Fernando Valley
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 28 at 9:23AM PST until January 30 at 3:00PM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 mph with gusts up to 45 mph
expected.

* WHERE...San Fernando Valley.

* WHEN...From 6 PM this evening to 3 PM PST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM THIS EVENING TO 3 PM PST THURSDAY
